title: "sub"
description: "Represents subscript text for chemical formulas, mathematical notation, and variable subscripts. Uses font-variant-position for proper OpenType rendering."
elementName: sub
category: native
nativeGroup: Text Semantics
currentPath: /docs/elements/native/sub/
permalink: /docs/elements/native/sub/
